These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: lavender, white, purple
1. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who likes white##1
2. the person who likes purple is between the person who likes lavender and the person who likes white##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |
| Color   | lavender | purple | white |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-2::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: aconite, begonia, sunflower
1. the person who growsaconite is between the person who growsbegonia and the person who growssunflower##2
2. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Flower   | sunflower | aconite | begonia |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-3::.
There 3 different types of food: grapefruit, zucchini, cauliflower
1. the person eating zucchini is between the person eating grapefruit and the person eating cauliflower##2
2. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |    3    |
| Food   | cauliflower | zucchini | grapefruit |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, board-games, hiking
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who's hobby is reading##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2   |     3      |
| Hobby   | reading | hiking | board-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-5::.
